ness/travel/spirit-airlines-doomed-sky-high-fuel-prices-due-recent-geopolitical-ev-rcna343466</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/travel/spirit-airlines-doomed-sky-high-fuel-prices-due-recent-geopolitical-ev-rcna343466</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-spirit-airlines-ew-1126a-8debc2.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Giorgio Viera</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Spirit Airlines</media:text><media:description type="plain">Spirit Airlines jets sit on the tarmac as the company ceased operations at Fort Lauderdale-Hollywood International Airport in Fort Lauderdale, Fla., on May 2, 2026. </media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-spirit-airlines-ew-1126a-8debc2.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 17:00:36 GMT</pubDate><title>Spirit Airlines doomed by high fuel prices due to &#39;recent geopolitical events,&#39; court docs state</title><updateDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 17:00:36 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Mon, 04 May 2026 20:29:50 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Britney Spears accepts plea deal in connection to DUI</description><expires>2056-05-04T20:28:39.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">f_vert_brk_spears_260504</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/video/shorts/britney-spears-accepts-plea-deal-in-connection-to-dui-262687301692</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/f_vert_brk_spears_260504/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Britney Spears accepts plea deal in connection to DUI</media:title><media:player url="https://www.nbcnews.com/video/shorts/britney-spears-accepts-plea-deal-in-connection-to-dui-262687301692"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/uploa